products.title: Breathable Adjustable Snack Back Trucker Hat Thin Cap For Men Women
products.description:
eBay
Feature:
1.Comes with thin quick dry material. This cap can help you feel more comfortable, especially after you sweat
2.Mesh cap is so breathable that it can help you feel cool when you are wearing it
3.The brim in the front can shield you from the sun and harmful ultraviolet rays. Protects your skin and eyes
4.Can be wiped. Can be compressed. Portable. Such features allow you to carry it when you are running, doing golf, playing tennis, going fishing, hiking, camping, sail boating, walking and even on the beach or other places
5.Lightweight cap can be adjusted to meet the needs of both men and women. When your friend forgets carrying the hat and you have the spare one, you can send it directly to your friend without considering if it is a right cap
6.Package include; 1 Cap
